<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   At New York News
   Threat of Strike
   Is Looming Larger
   ----
   By Patrick M. Reilly
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/02/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7G
